data.enText: a large sea fish that is used for food

data.chText: 一罐植物油浸金枪鱼罐头
data.enText: a tin/can of tuna in vegetable oil

tr: any very large marine food and game fish of the genus Thunnus
important warm-water fatty fish of the genus Thunnus of the family Scombridae
tropical American prickly pear of Jamaica

value.def: Tuna or tuna fish are large fish that live in warm seas and are caught for food.

posc.def: Tuna or tuna fish is this fish eaten as food.

example.ex: She began opening a tin of tuna.
example.tran: 她开始打开一听金枪鱼罐头。
